Welcome to the minimal site starter!

This site is build with Sass - to get all set up please follow the following instructions:
-  You will need Node (see installation instructions here: https://nodejs.org) and Gulp (see installation instructions here: http://gulpjs.com/)
-  From the command line, cd into your new site root
-  Run "npm install"
-  Run "npm update caniuse-db"
-  Run "gulp"
-  To stop watching, use Ctrl+C

